title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2007-09 Toyota Camry Projector Headlights w/ LED DRLs
description: This instructional how-to video is designed to demonstrate how to properly install a set of Spyder Auto projector headlights on 2007 through 2009 model Toyota Camry vehicles. Unfortunately these do not fit 2010-11 models. This complete walkthrough will guide you through the entire install process, including removing the front bumper fascia (it sounds scary, but it's not at all) and all bolt/fastener locations and sizes.
tags: Spyder Projector Headlights, Toyota Camry, how to install spyder headlights, Camry projector headlights
